<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Organizer Dashboard - Hackathon Platform</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #f85454);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding-top: 80px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        nav {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #f85454);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        nav h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin: 0 1rem;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }

        .profile-icon {
            position: relative;
        }

        .profile-icon img {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .dropdown-menu {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            top: 40px;
            right: 0;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .dropdown-menu a {
            display: block;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .dropdown-menu a:hover {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .welcome-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 2rem;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .intro-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 50px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: nowrap;
        }

        .image-section img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .content-section {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: 40px;
        }

        .content-section h1 {
            color: #e84343;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .content-section p {
            color: #34495e;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .success-message {
            color: #2ecc71;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .error-message {
            color: #e74c3c;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav ul {
                flex-direction: column;
                background-color: #2563eb;
                position: absolute;
                top: 60px;
                right: 0;
                width: 200px;
                display: none;
                border-radius: 8px;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            }

            nav ul.show {
                display: flex;
            }

            nav ul li {
                margin: 0.8rem 0;
            }

            .menu-toggle {
                display: block;
                cursor: pointer;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .intro-section {
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .content-section {
                margin-left: 0;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }

            .welcome-header {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
        }

        .menu-toggle {
            display: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <h1>Hackathon Platform</h1>
        <div class="menu-toggle">☰</div>
        <ul>
            <% if (user) { %>
                <li><a href="/organizer">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/addEvent">Event Management</a></li>
                <li><a href="/hosting">Updated Events</a></li>
                <li><a href="/announcements">Announcements</a></li>
                <li class="profile-icon">
                    <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/847/847969.png" alt="Profile" id="profileIcon">
                    <div class="dropdown-menu" id="dropdownMenu">
                        <a href="/profile">Profile</a>
                        <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
            <% } else { %>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
            <% } %>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <% if (user) { %>
            <h2 class="welcome-header">Welcome, <%= user.name %></h2>
            <div class="intro-section">
                <div class="image-section">
                    <img src="/hackthon_img.jpg" alt="Hackathon Image">
                </div>
                <div class="content-section">
                    <h1>Hackathon</h1>
                    <p>
                        A hackathon is an event where individuals or teams collaborate intensively over a short period—often 24 to 48 hours—to develop innovative solutions, software, or products. It’s a space for creative minds, including developers, designers, and problem-solvers, to brainstorm, code, and prototype ideas that address specific challenges or explore new concepts. Hackathons encourage teamwork, rapid problem-solving, and out-of-the-box thinking, fostering an environment of innovation and learning.
                    </p>
                    <!-- <% if (success) { %>
                        <p class="success-message"><%= success %></p>
                    <% } %>
                    <% if (error) { %>
                        <p class="error-message"><%= error %></p>
                    <% } %> -->
                </div>
            </div>
        <% } else { %>
            <h2 class="welcome-header">Please Log In</h2>
            <div class="intro-section">
                <p style="color: #34495e; text-align: center;">You need to be logged in to access the organizer dashboard. <a href="/login" style="color: #6a11cb;">Login here</a>.</p>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>

    <script>
        const menuToggle = document.querySelector('.menu-toggle');
        const navLinks = document.querySelector('nav ul');
        const profileIcon = document.getElementById('profileIcon');
        const dropdownMenu = document.getElementById('dropdownMenu');

        menuToggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
            navLinks.classList.toggle('show');
        });

        if (profileIcon) { // Only add listener if profileIcon exists
            profileIcon.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
                dropdownMenu.style.display = dropdownMenu.style.display === 'block' ? 'none' : 'block';
            });

            window.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                if (!profileIcon.contains(e.target) && !dropdownMenu.contains(e.target)) {
                    dropdownMenu.style.display = 'none';
                }
            });
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>